annotations.title: 5 EASY GIN COCKTAIL RECIPES!

textContent:
2 oz gin
0.5 oz Maraschino
0.75 oz Lemon juice
0.25 oz Simple syrup
3 Dashes Orange Angostura bitters

Shake and strain into coupe
Garnish with Maraschino cherry
